 54→ * @example
 55→ * ```tsx
 56→ * const MyComponent = () => {
 57→ *   const fetchData = useCallback((timeSpan?: TimeSpan) => {
 58→ *     // fetch data...
 59→ *   }, []);
 60→ *
 61→ *   useDashboardRefresh(fetchData);
 62→ *
 63→ *   return <div>...</div>;
 64→ * };
 65→ * ```
